query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!"
        FROM clerk_queue
        WHERE court_id = $1
          AND ($2::TEXT IS NULL OR status = $2)
          AND ($3::TEXT IS NULL OR queue_type = $3)
          AND ($4::INT IS NULL OR priority = $4)
          AND ($5::BIGINT IS NULL OR assigned_to = $5)
          AND ($6::UUID IS NULL OR case_id = $6)
